        <indexterm>Shortcut actions in Text Mode</indexterm>
        <indexterm>Font size configuration in Text mode</indexterm>
        <indexterm>Changing the font size in Text mode</indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p><ph keyref="product"/> includes numerous shortcut actions to help you edit content in the
        <uicontrol>Text</uicontrol> editing mode.</p>
    <section conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/font-size-section"
      product="author developer editor" id="changing-font-size"/>
    <section conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/undo-redo-section" id="d2e28"/>
    <section conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/copy-paste-section" id="d2e30"/>
    <section id="miscellaneous_shortcut_actions_in_text_mode">
      <title>Miscellaneous Shortcut Actions in Text Mode</title>
      <p><ph keyref="product"/> also includes the following other miscellaneous shortcut actions in
          <uicontrol>Text</uicontrol> mode:</p>
      <p>
        <dl>
          <dlentry>
            <dt><uicontrol conkeyref="reusable_oxygen_shortcuts_list/ctrl_delete"/></dt>
            <dd>Deletes the next word.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry>
            <dt><uicontrol conkeyref="reusable_oxygen_shortcuts_list/ctrl_backspace"/></dt>
            <dd>Deletes the previous word.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry>
            <dt><uicontrol conkeyref="reusable_oxygen_shortcuts_list/ctrl_w"/></dt>
            <dd>Cuts the previous word.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry>
            <dt><uicontrol conkeyref="reusable_oxygen_shortcuts_list/ctrl_k"/></dt>
            <dd>Cuts to end of line.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry>
            <dt><uicontrol conkeyref="reusable_oxygen_shortcuts_list/ctrl_click"/></dt>
            <dd>Use this shortcut to open any of the following:<ul id="ul_2tr_xh2_zf">
                <li>Any absolute URL (URLs that have a protocol), regardless of their location in
                  the document.</li>
                <li>URI attributes such as: <term>schemaLocation</term>,
                    <term>noNamespaceSchemaLocation</term>, <term>href</term> and others.</li>
                <li>Processing instructions used for associating resources, xml-models,
                  xml-stylesheets. </li>
              </ul></dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry>
            <dt><uicontrol conkeyref="reusable_oxygen_shortcuts_list/ctrl_shift_y"/> (<menucascade>
                <uicontrol>Document</uicontrol>
                <uicontrol>Edit</uicontrol>
                <uicontrol>Toggle Line Wrap</uicontrol>
              </menucascade>)</dt>
            <dd> Enables or disables line wrapping. When enabled, if text exceeds the width of the
              displayed editor, content is wrapped so that you do not have to scroll
              horizontally.</dd>
          </dlentry>
        </dl>
      </p>
    </section>
  </body>
